nt":21,"license":null,"allow_forking":true,"is_template":false,"web_commit_signoff_required":false,"has_pull_requests":true,"pull_request_creation_policy":"all","topics":[],"visibility":"public","forks":136,"open_issues":21,"watchers":901,"default_branch":"master"}},"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.github.com/repos/doldecomp/melee/pulls/2540"},"html":{"href":"https://github.com/doldecomp/melee/pull/2540"},"issue":{"href":"https://api.github.com/repos/doldecomp/melee/issues/2540"},"comments":{"href":"https://api.github.com/repos/doldecomp/melee/issues/2540/comments"},"review_comments":{"href":"https://api.github.com/repos/doldecomp/melee/pulls/2540/comments"},"review_comment":{"href":"https://api.github.com/repos/doldecomp/melee/pulls/comments{/number}"},"commits":{"href":"https://api.github.com/repos/doldecomp/melee/pulls/2540/commits"},"statuses":{"href":"https://api.github.com/repos/doldecomp/melee/statuses/c61afd3491b1721c0d33c41e6153b537b0fcd775"}},"author_association":"COLLABORATOR","auto_merge":{"enabled_by":{"login":"jellejurre","id":76777936,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjc2Nzc3OTM2","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/76777936?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/jellejurre","html_url":"https://github.com/jellejurre","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jellejurre/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jellejurre/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jellejurre/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jellejurre/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jellejurre/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jellejurre/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jellejurre/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jellejurre/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jellejurre/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"merge_method":"squash","commit_title":"Jj/sislib (#2540)","commit_message":"* Match HSD_SisLib_803A594C (92%)\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>\n\n* Match HSD_SisLib_803A5798 (99%)\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>\n\n* Match HSD_SisLib_803A7F0C (98%)\n\nMerge the pointer-param inline into a single function so pos/result/remove_size\nstay in registers, and byte-index string_buffer (s16 signed for type 1, u16\nunsigned for type 3). Remaining diffs are register swaps and an 8-byte frame.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>\n\n* Match HSD_SisLib_803A8134 (94%)\n\nFix halfword cursor reads (s16/u16 not byte/float), case 0/8 cursor reassign,\npass cursor pointer to HSD_SisLib_803A7684, relocate block_33, while-loop the\ntail clear. Remaining diffs are the HSD_SisLib_8040CB00 SDA-vs-hoist register\ncascade and an add reassociation.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>\n\n* Match HSD_SisLib_803A67EC (60%)\n\nImplement the ASCII->SIS conversion: fill in the space/dot/digit/colon kerning\nprefix blocks, the SJIS LUT lookup loop (lbl_8040C8C0 -> HSD_SisLib_8040C680),\nand convert to a for-loop. Remaining diffs are register allocation (has_kerning\nstack spill vs register, CTR loop) producing extra moves.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>\n\n* Match HSD_SisLib_803A70A0 (79%)\n\nImplement the entry-replace function: find entry via fn_803A6FEC, format with\nvsnprintf+HSD_SisLib_803A67EC, grow/shrink the buffer and shift the tail, then\ncopy the encoded string in. Remaining diffs are loop form (CTR vs manual\ndecrement) and bulk-8 unroll style.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>\n\n* Match HSD_SisLib_803A6B98 (87%)\n\nFix the append-entry function: write through alloc->data_0 as the byte cursor\n(member reload/increment per write), use (s16)x/(s16)y for position, correct\ncolor/scale header order, and per-byte bulk copy. Remaining diffs are CTR loop\nform and register allocation.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>\n\n* Match HSD_SisLib_803A7684 (55%)\n\nImplement the push-state function: 5-case switch (scale/color/scale2/align/value)\nthat ensures string_buffer room (realloc + bulk copy + zero-fill) then writes the\nstate bytes via x6C++. Remaining diffs are CTR loop form and post-increment\nregister allocation in the copy loops.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>\n\n* Match HSD_SisLib_803A84BC (89%)\n\nAdd the HSD_SisLib_803A8134 line-measure call in opcode 7, and fix the delay\n(case 5/6 u16) and scale (case 10 s16, case 14 u16) cursor reads to halfword.\nRemaining diffs are the HSD_SisLib_8040CD40/CB00 SDA-vs-hoist register cascade.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>\n\n* Remove target funcs\n\n---------\n\nCo-authored-by: Claude Opus 4.7 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>\nCo-authored-by: jellejurre <git@jellejurre.dev>\nCo-authored-by: JelleJurre <76777936+jellejurre@users.noreply.github.com>"},"assignee":null,"active_lock_reason":null,"merged":true,"mergeable":null,"rebaseable":null,"mergeable_state":"unknown","merged_by":{"login":"jellejurre","id":76777936,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjc2Nzc3OTM2","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/76777936?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/jellejurre","html_url":"https://github.com/jellejurre","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jellejurre/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jellejurre/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jellejurre/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jellejurre/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jellejurre/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jellejurre/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jellejurre/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jellejurre/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jellejurre/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"comments":1,"review_comments":0,"maintainer_can_modify":false,"commits":12,"additions":717,"deletions":411,"changed_files":2}